         <unitdate unitdatetype="inclusive">circa 1900-1950</unitdate>
         <abstract id="aspace_b75fd1c175c286be8ab0b2f15af0116b">The collection consists of souvenir postcards of Yale, most of which depict buildings and grounds. Also included are postcards depicting Yale athletics, symbols, and student life.</abstract>
